data.description: Experience the splendor of one of the most exquisite properties located in the heart of Westbury, one of Houston's most sought-after neighborhoods. This grand, two-story residence offers flexible living spaces and is situated on a massive lot providing ample outdoor space in both the front and back yards.?The house boasts designer finishes and energy-efficient upgrades, culminating in an ideal environment for entertaining or relaxation. The sunroom, adorned with abundant natural light and serene views of the backyard, serves as the perfect retreat to unwind.
